                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="projects-wrapper">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="projects-header">
          <h4 class="section-title">Explore our diverse range of projects</h4>
          <p class="section-subtitle">
          From residential buildings to government infrastructure, explore our diverse project portfolio spanning structural design, audits, and detailed consultancy.
